node.text: Bugs on your front end taking away at the overall look of your ride? Don’t use harsh cleaners that can damage or scratch your ride to remove them, use Bug & Tar Remover Wash! Stay tuned until the end of the video to see these incredible results!

node.title: HOW TO REMOVE BUGS FROM YOUR RIDE!
